Class AbstractTigrContigBuilderVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.tigr.contig.AbstractTigrContigBuilderVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TigrContigVisitor

    public abstract class AbstractTigrContigBuilderVisitor
extends Object
implements TigrContigVisitor
    AbstractTigrContigBuilderVisitor is a TigrContigVisitor that will create a TigrContigBuilder and populate it using the visit calls.

      • visitContig

        protected abstract void visitContig(TigrContigBuilder builder)
        The entire contig has been visited. This method will only be called from inside visitEnd(). Subclasses may modify the builder as they see fit.
        Parameters:
        builder - a completely populated TigrContigBuilder instance containing all the contig data gathered from the visit methods; will never be null.
